{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"志新，“七一”到了！","authors":["郝玉芝"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":6,"day":30}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"志新，“七一”到了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郝玉芝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志新，“七一”到了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这光辉灿烂的日子里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈的心情是多么地激动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈是多么地思念你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈有多少话想向你倾诉……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五一年的“七一”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你在革命熔炉人民大学里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刻苦学习马列主义，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"认真探求着真理。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你拿出一张白纸，一支钢笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀着一颗纯洁、火热的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向伟大、光荣、正确的党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写下金光闪闪的誓言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为共产主义奋斗终身，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永不叛党，永不动摇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你给妈写信："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我在‘七一’向党"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交了第一份申请书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿把一切献给党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈，您应当为我感到高兴。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九七○年的“七一”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，在暗无天日的监狱里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"受尽了残酷的迫害，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚持着英勇的斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"真理呀，真理！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个共产党员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要实践对党的誓言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚定不移地捍卫您！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你拿出一小束白纸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀着对光明前途无限"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为伟大、光荣、正确的党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扎了一朵举世无双的小红花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浸透着对敌人全部的恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包含着对人民全部的爱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，戴着小红花，站在铁窗前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚韧地度过黑暗的夜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来了“七一”的朝霞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧！铁窗外的红日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和你胸襟上的红花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"互相辉映。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，不能给妈写信，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，妈却听到了你的心音："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我在‘七一’向党表了心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为革命作出贡献，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给孩子作出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"榜样的时刻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经来到！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿把生命献给党！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈，您应当为我感到骄傲。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志新，“七一”又到了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，一九七九年的“七一”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，默默地长眠在地下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浩气不断升华，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党给你以烈士的光荣称号，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民在悼念你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民在歌颂你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的精神，你的榜样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正化为滚滚的热潮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志新！听妈告诉你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们伟大的祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在打倒万恶“四人帮”的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三年时间里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呈现出日新月异的面貌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党恢复了青春活力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"领导全国人民朝着四化迅跑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孩子！你的心愿实现了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是，你又在哪里？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！妈看见了你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你飞奔在四化的行列里！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈为你感到高兴！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈为你感到骄傲！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}